item.title: About Me
item.description: Welcome to my website. My name is John Elizarraras. I am a high school student. Most of these projects are just things I work on for fun and probably have been created before. To view links please click on the blog post.

item.title: PyMathTools
item.description: PyMathTools is a module writing in python. It has more functions that can be a substitute for sage and others. It is a lightweight solution for doing more advanced math. The repo is here.

item.title: advanced planner
item.description: This is my 20% project. It was originally a tool that would have special commands for the terminal but it just turned into a timing mechanism. You can view it here.
